            "label": "Judgement",
            "description": "A judgement is a type of focus spell unique to the zealot class. A judgement focus spell is cast like any other, except that it can only be cast in combat. Additionally a zealot may not have more than one judgement spell active at the same time. Should the zealot cast a new judgement spell while another is still active, the duration and effect of the previous judgement spell ends immediately. Some class feats may allow you to have multiple judgements active at once."
